    #howitworks.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='myModalLabel', aria-hidden='true')
      .modal-dialog.modal-lg
        .modal-content
          .modal-header
            button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-hidden='true') &times;
            h4#myModalLabel.modal-title How It Works
          .modal-body
            p BitSplit is a bitcoin micro-lottery where larger total bets have a disproportionately higher chance of winning.

            p It&apos;s a lottery where you can consistently earn money if you play strategically.

            p Play around with the pretend money you received for signing up, and see the game in action!

            p If you&apos;re feeling feisty, try to steal some real money from the bitcoin pot with the 1 satoshi you&apos;ve been given :).
          .modal-footer
            button.btn.btn-default(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') Close
